<item>
            <title>[FLINK-8420] Timeout exceptions are not properly recognized by RetryingRegistration</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-8420</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;RetryingRegistration&lt;/tt&gt; does not correctly respond to &lt;tt&gt;TimeoutExceptions&lt;/tt&gt; and instead treats them like errors. This causes that it waits for the delay on error instead of backing exponentially off.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13130513">FLINK-8420</key>
