&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;commit 08a4788572de57b9878c95b45d6c2a0256691a4f&lt;br/&gt;
Author: Till Rohrmann &amp;lt;trohrmann@...&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Date:   2018-01-03T12:25:09Z&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-8340&quot; title=&quot;Do not pass Configuration and configuration directory to CustomCommandLine methods&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-8340&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-8340&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;flip6&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Remove passing of Configuration to CustomCommandLine&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Since the Configuration does not change over the lifetime of a CustomCommandLine,&lt;br/&gt;
    we can safely pass it as a constructor argument instead of method argument.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    This closes #5226.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;commit 20bf4f179239c9e29bad75433859f45738b260fe&lt;br/&gt;
